netistrar.clientapi.objects.utility

Class BulkOperationProgress

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.utility.BulkOperationProgress

  • public class BulkOperationProgress
extends java.lang.Object
    Encodes information about the current progress of a bulk operation. This includes the status of all contained BulkOperationProgressItem objects which make up the bulk operation as well as general information about the progress of the whole operation both as a percentage and as a number of completed items for use in progressively updating GUIs etc.
